node.text:
Real hot girl energy starts with self-care ladiessss. Always prioritizing taking care of your body is so, so important. Today, I wanted to quickly talk about the Pap test and potential new guidelines, which would limit access to this life saving test for women under 25 years old. Did you know that every hour, 1 woman in the U.S is diagnosed with cervical cancer? 
 
The Pap test has saved thousands of lives from cervical cancer. Every person with a cervix deserves access to this life saving test. Learn more at 25andalive.org✨ #25andalive #sponsored
 
In Partnership with The Social Good Foundation
